OUTPUT DIR: /Users/steve/Documents/3SK/outputs/06_CEO/Org_Briefs

ORG STRUCTURE (from /Volumes/AI_Workspace/iris_studio/dashboard/org_chart.json):
  CEO: chief-executive (opus) — rolls up the five department briefs.
